text:
This Feb, the 90,000-seat #Sambódromo is empty due to #COVID19 ☹️

Instead of uninterrupted parties, #Carnival this year is marked by the giant art installation “#TodosPelasVacinas (All for Vaccines)” created by local young people.

Youth are key in driving #vaccine confidence 💪 https://t.co/ZdoYLfrfuu
